            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#0A2F5C] text-[#B28D42] font-bold mb-4">✓</span>
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-slate-800 text-lg">Obra limpa e rápida</span>
